milestones.description: Zaheer Khan has become the top wicket-taker for ASIA in ODIs with 5 wickets, going past Murali's 3
Abdul Razzaq has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for ASIA, going past Rahul Dravid
Anil Kumble and Abdul Razzaq's 56-run partnership is ASIA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Chaminda Vaas and Rahul Dravid
